The species was previously known from Kyrgyzstan, Uzbekistan, Turkmenistan (
Marusik 1989
; 
Mikhailov 2013
), and Xinjiang, China (
Marusik et al. 2007
). A search for literature records reveals that it was reported also from southeastern Kazakhstan (sub. 
M. orientalis
: 
Spassky 1952
). New material studied in this work reveals its occurrence in Tajikistan and eastern Azerbaijan (Fig. 47).
